linear regression for Funksvd

for (i in 1:n) {
  da<-cbind(genre,Funksvd[,i])
  name<-colnames(genre)
  name1<-c(name,"mu")
  colnames(da)<-name1
  da<-as.data.frame(da)
  barplot(lm(mu~.,data=da)$coefficients[-c(1,2)],las=2)
  title(paste("Funksvd factor",i))
}

  da<-as.data.frame(da)
  barplot(lm(mu~.,data=da)$coefficients[-c(1,2)],las=2)

}
